hadiths[223]{hadithnumber,text}:
6500,"Sabit Bunani ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aaj raat mera aik betaa paida hua hai jiska naam maine apne walid ke naam par Ibrahim rakha hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us bachchey ko abu saif naam ke lohar ki biwi umme-Saif (Raziallahu anhu) ke sipurd kar diya, phir (eik roz) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us bachchey ke paas janey ke liye chal padey mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey chala ham abu-Yusuf ke paas pahunchey wo bhatti phoonk raha tha. ghar dhoein se bhara hua tha. main tezi se chalta hua Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aagey ho gaya aur kaha : abu saif ! ruk jao, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey hain, wo ruk gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bachchey ko mangwa bheja , aap ne usey apne sath laga liya aur jo Allah chahta tha, aap ne farmaya (mohabbat w shafqat ke bol boley.) to Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine us bachchey ko dekha, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki aankhon) ke samney apni jaan jaane-aafreen ke sipurd kar raha tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon mein aansu aa gaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aankhen aansu baha rahi hain aur dil gham se bhara hua hai lekin ham iske siwa aur kuchh nahi kahengey jis se hamara parwardigar razi ho, Allah ki qism ! Ibrahim ! ham aap ki) judai ki) wjah se sakht ghamzada hain."
6501,"Sabit Bunani ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aaj raat mera aik betaa paida hua hai jiska naam maine apne walid ke naam par Ibrahim rakha hai. phir Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us bachchey ko abu saif naam ke lohar ki biwi umme-Saif (Raziallahu anhu) ke sipurd kar diya, phir (eik roz) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us bachchey ke paas janey ke liye chal padey mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke peechhey chala ham abu-Yusuf ke paas pahunchey wo bhatti phoonk raha tha. ghar dhoein se bhara hua tha. main tezi se chalta hua Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aagey ho gaya aur kaha : abu saif ! ruk jao, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif laey hain, wo ruk gaya. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne bachchey ko mangwa bheja , aap ne usey apne sath laga liya aur jo Allah chahta tha, aap ne farmaya (mohabbat w shafqat ke bol boley.) to Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine us bachchey ko dekha, wo Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (ki aankhon) ke samney apni jaan jaane-aafreen ke sipurd kar raha tha to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki aankhon mein aansu aa gaey, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aankhen aansu baha rahi hain aur dil gham se bhara hua hai lekin ham iske siwa aur kuchh nahi kahengey jis se hamara parwardigar razi ho, Allah ki qism ! Ibrahim ! ham aap ki) judai ki) wjah se sakht ghamzada hain."
6502,"Amr bin Saeed ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se badh kar kisi ko apni aulad par shafeeq nahi dekha, (aap ke farzand) Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) Madina ki oopri basti mein doodh peetey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan tashrif ley jatey aur ham bhi aap ke sath hotey they, aap ghar mein dakhil hotey to wahan dhuaan hota kyonke Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ka dudh-sharik walid lohar tha. aap bachchey ko letey, usey piyaar kartey aur phir lot aatey. Amr (bin Saeed) ne kaha : jab Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Ibrahim mera beta hai aur wo doodh peeney ke dinon mein faut hua hai, uski doodh pilaaney wali 2 maain hain jo jannat mein uski doodh pilaney (ki muddat ( mukammal karengi."
6503,"Amr bin Saeed ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se badh kar kisi ko apni aulad par shafeeq nahi dekha, (aap ke farzand) Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) Madina ki oopri basti mein doodh peetey they, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) wahan tashrif ley jatey aur ham bhi aap ke sath hotey they, aap ghar mein dakhil hotey to wahan dhuaan hota kyonke Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) ka dudh-sharik walid lohar tha. aap bachchey ko letey, usey piyaar kartey aur phir lot aatey. Amr (bin Saeed) ne kaha : jab Hazrat Ibrahim (Raziallahu anhu) faut ho gaey to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Ibrahim mera beta hai aur wo doodh peeney ke dinon mein faut hua hai, uski doodh pilaaney wali 2 maain hain jo jannat mein uski doodh pilaney (ki muddat ( mukammal karengi."
6504,"abu-Usama aur ibne-Numair ne Hisham (bin Urwa ( se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baadiya se kuchh log aaey aur unhon-ne puchha : kya aap log apne bachchon ko kuchh bosa detey hain? logon ne kaha : haan , to un logon ne kaha : lekin Allah ki qism ! ham to apne bachchon ko bosa nahi detey, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar Allah Taala ne tumharey andar se rehmat nikal di hai (to kya ho sakta hai ! ( ibne-Numair ki riwayat mein hai : tumharey dil se rehmat nikal di hai."
6505,"abu-Usama aur ibne-Numair ne Hisham (bin Urwa ( se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas baadiya se kuchh log aaey aur unhon-ne puchha : kya aap log apne bachchon ko kuchh bosa detey hain? logon ne kaha : haan , to un logon ne kaha : lekin Allah ki qism ! ham to apne bachchon ko bosa nahi detey, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : agar Allah Taala ne tumharey andar se rehmat nikal di hai (to kya ho sakta hai ! ( ibne-Numair ki riwayat mein hai : tumharey dil se rehmat nikal di hai."
6506,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Aqra-bin-Habis (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ko bosa de rahe they, unhon-ne kaha : mere das bachchey hain aur maine unmein se kisi ko kabhi bosa nahi diya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs raham nahi karta is par raham nahi kya jaeyga."
6507,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Zohri se, unhon-ne abu-Salma se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Aqra-bin-Habis (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, aap Hazrat Hasan (Raziallahu anhu) ko bosa de rahe they, unhon-ne kaha : mere das bachchey hain aur maine unmein se kisi ko kabhi bosa nahi diya, to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs raham nahi karta is par raham nahi kya jaeyga."
6508,"Mamar ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6509,"Mamar ne Zohri se riwayat ki, kaha : mujhey abu-Salma ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6510,"Jareer, Esa-bin-Yonus, abu-Muawiya aur Hafs bin Ghiyas sab ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Zaid-bin Wahab aur abu-Zibyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jareer-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs logon par raham nahi karta izzat aur jalaal waala Allah is par rehem nahi karta."
6511,"Jareer, Esa-bin-Yonus, abu-Muawiya aur Hafs bin Ghiyas sab ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Zaid-bin Wahab aur abu-Zibyan se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jareer-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs logon par raham nahi karta izzat aur jalaal waala Allah is par rehem nahi karta."
6512,"Qais aur Naafe bin Juber ne Jarir se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Aamash ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6513,"Qais aur Naafe bin Juber ne Jarir se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se Aamash ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6514,"Abdullah-bin-Ubai Utba ne kaha : maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us kunwari ladki se zyada haya karne waley they jo pardey mein hoti hai. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi cheez ko na-pasand farmatey to hamein aap ke chehrey se iska pata chal jata."
6515,"Abdullah-bin-Ubai Utba ne kaha : maine Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, keh rahe they : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) us kunwari ladki se zyada haya karne waley they jo pardey mein hoti hai. jab Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) kisi cheez ko na-pasand farmatey to hamein aap ke chehrey se iska pata chal jata."
6516,"Zohri bin Harab aur Usman bin abi Sheba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Shaqiq se, unhon-ne Masruq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) Kufa aaey to ham (unke sath aaney waale) Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se ja kar miley, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr kya aur kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) na taban zaban se koi buri baat nikalney waley they aur na takalluf karke bura kehney waley they, neez unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein sabse achchhey log wahi hain jo akhlaq mein sabse achchhey hain. Usman (bin abi Sheba) ne kaha : jis mauqe par Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Kufa aaey they."
6517,"Zohri bin Harab aur Usman bin abi Sheba ne hamein hadis bayan ki, donon ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Shaqiq se, unhon-ne Masruq se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) Kufa aaey to ham (unke sath aaney waale) Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) se ja kar miley, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka zikr kya aur kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) na taban zaban se koi buri baat nikalney waley they aur na takalluf karke bura kehney waley they, neez unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein sabse achchhey log wahi hain jo akhlaq mein sabse achchhey hain. Usman (bin abi Sheba) ne kaha : jis mauqe par Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Amr (Raziallahu anhu) Hazrat Muawiya (Raziallahu anhu) ke sath Kufa aaey they."
6518,"abu-Muawiya, Wakee, Abdullah-bin-Numair aur abu-Khalid Ahmar, un sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
6519,"abu-Muawiya, Wakee, Abdullah-bin-Numair aur abu-Khalid Ahmar, un sab ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
6520,"Samak-bin-Harab se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein shirkat kartey they? unhon-ne kaha : haan, bahut shirkat ki, aap jis jagah par subah ki Namaz padhtey they, to suraj nikalney se pahley wahan se nahi uthtey they. jab suraj nikal aata to aap wahan se uthtey, sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) jahiliyat ke (kisi na kisi) mamley ko letey aur (is par aapasi) baat cheet kartey to hansi mazaaq bhi kartey, ( lekin) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( sirf ( muskuratey they."
6521,"Samak-bin-Harab se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jaabir bin Samra (Raziallahu anhu) se puchha : kya aap Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki majlis mein shirkat kartey they? unhon-ne kaha : haan, bahut shirkat ki, aap jis jagah par subah ki Namaz padhtey they, to suraj nikalney se pahley wahan se nahi uthtey they. jab suraj nikal aata to aap wahan se uthtey, sahaba kiram (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) jahiliyat ke (kisi na kisi) mamley ko letey aur (is par aapasi) baat cheet kartey to hansi mazaaq bhi kartey, ( lekin) Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ( sirf ( muskuratey they."
6522,"Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar mein they aur aik habshi ghulam jiska naam Anjasha tha wo achchi aawaz mein Hadi padhnewala tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey anjasha ! ahista-ahista chal, aur oonton ko sheeshey ladey oonton ki tarah haank.''"
6523,"Saiyedna Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) safar mein they aur aik habshi ghulam jiska naam Anjasha tha wo achchi aawaz mein Hadi padhnewala tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ''aey anjasha ! ahista-ahista chal, aur oonton ko sheeshey ladey oonton ki tarah haank.''"
6524,"Hammad ne hamein Sabit se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
6525,"Hammad ne hamein Sabit se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
6526,"Ismail (bin Mina ( ne kaha : hamein Ayub ne abu-Qilaba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni beeviyon ke paas gaey, us waqt Anjasha naam ka aik oont haankney wala un (ke oonton) ko haank raha tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Anjasha tum par afsos! sheeshe (jaisi nazuk khawaateen) ko aahisatagi aur aaraam se chalaao. Ayub ne kaha : abu-Qilaba ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa kalima bola ke agar tum mein se koi aisa kalima kehta to tum is par aib lagaatey ."
6527,"Ismail (bin Mina ( ne kaha : hamein Ayub ne abu-Qilaba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apni beeviyon ke paas gaey, us waqt Anjasha naam ka aik oont haankney wala un (ke oonton) ko haank raha tha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Anjasha tum par afsos! sheeshe (jaisi nazuk khawaateen) ko aahisatagi aur aaraam se chalaao. Ayub ne kaha : abu-Qilaba ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne aisa kalima bola ke agar tum mein se koi aisa kalima kehta to tum is par aib lagaatey ."
6528,"Sulaiman Taimi ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki, kaha : Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon ke sath thin aur aik oont haankney wala unke oont haank raha tha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Anjasha! sheeshe (jaisi nazuk khawaateen) ko aahisatagi aur aa raam se chalaao ."
6529,"Sulaiman Taimi ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki, kaha : Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) bhi Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki beeviyon ke sath thin aur aik oont haankney wala unke oont haank raha tha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Anjasha! sheeshe (jaisi nazuk khawaateen) ko aahisatagi aur aa raam se chalaao ."
6530,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aik achchi aawaz mein hadi padhnewala tha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : Anjasha ! aaraam se (haanko) sheeshon ko mat todo, yani kamzor aurton ko."
6531,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat bayan ki, kaha : Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ka aik achchi aawaz mein hadi padhnewala tha, Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : Anjasha ! aaraam se (haanko) sheeshon ko mat todo, yani kamzor aurton ko."
6532,"Hisham ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki aur is mein achchi awaz mein hadi padhnewaley ka zikr nahi kya."
6533,"Hisham ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki aur is mein achchi awaz mein hadi padhnewaley ka zikr nahi kya."
6534,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab subah ki Namaz se farigh hotey to Madina ke khaadim (ghulam) apne bartan ley aatey jin mein pani hota, jo bhi bartan aap ke samney laya jata Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna hath usmein dubotey, kabhi-kabhi sakht thandi subah mein bartan laey jatey to aap ( phir bhi) unmein apna hath dubo detey."
6535,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) jab subah ki Namaz se farigh hotey to Madina ke khaadim (ghulam) apne bartan ley aatey jin mein pani hota, jo bhi bartan aap ke samney laya jata Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apna hath usmein dubotey, kabhi-kabhi sakht thandi subah mein bartan laey jatey to aap ( phir bhi) unmein apna hath dubo detey."
6536,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, baal moondney wala aap ke sar ke baal utaar raha tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) aap ke ird-gird they, wo nahi chahtey they ke aap ka koi bhi baal unmein se kisi aik ke hathon ke ilawa kahin aur girey."
6537,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, baal moondney wala aap ke sar ke baal utaar raha tha aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sahaba (Rizwaanullahi anhum ajmaeen) aap ke ird-gird they, wo nahi chahtey they ke aap ka koi bhi baal unmein se kisi aik ke hathon ke ilawa kahin aur girey."
6538,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aurat ki aql mein kuchh naqs tha (eik din) wo kehney lagi : Allah ke rasool! mujhey aap se kaam hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (bahut shafqat w ehtiraam se) farmaya : umme-falan! dekho, jis gali main tum chaho (khadi ho jaao) main (wahan aa kar) tumhara kaam kar dunga. aap aik rastey mein us se alag miley, yahan tak ke usne apna kaam kar liya."
6539,"Sabit ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik aurat ki aql mein kuchh naqs tha (eik din) wo kehney lagi : Allah ke rasool! mujhey aap se kaam hai. Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne (bahut shafqat w ehtiraam se) farmaya : umme-falan! dekho, jis gali main tum chaho (khadi ho jaao) main (wahan aa kar) tumhara kaam kar dunga. aap aik rastey mein us se alag miley, yahan tak ke usne apna kaam kar liya."
6540,"Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko 2 kaamon mein se (eik ka ( intikhab karna hota to aap un donon mein se zyada aasan ko muntakhab farmatey. basharte ke wo gunah na hota, agar wo gunah ka kaam hota to aap sab logon se badh kar us se door hotey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni khaatir kabhi kisi se intiqaam nahi liya, siwaey is sura ke ke Allah ki had ko todaa jata."
6541,"Imam Malik (Rehmatullahi-alaih) ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se, unhon-ne Nabi Karim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : jab bhi Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko 2 kaamon mein se (eik ka ( intikhab karna hota to aap un donon mein se zyada aasan ko muntakhab farmatey. basharte ke wo gunah na hota, agar wo gunah ka kaam hota to aap sab logon se badh kar us se door hotey . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni khaatir kabhi kisi se intiqaam nahi liya, siwaey is sura ke ke Allah ki had ko todaa jata."
6542,"Mansoor ne Muhammad se. Fuzel ki riwayat mein hai : ibne-Shahab se, Jarir ki riwayat mein hai : Muhammad Zohri se. unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se (yahi) riwayat bayan ki."
6543,"Mansoor ne Muhammad se. Fuzel ki riwayat mein hai : ibne-Shahab se, Jarir ki riwayat mein hai : Muhammad Zohri se. unhon-ne Urwa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se (yahi) riwayat bayan ki."
6544,Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath Imam Malik ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki.
6545,Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se isi sanad ke sath Imam Malik ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki.
6546,"abu-Usama ne Hisham (bin Urwa) se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab bhi 2 kaamon mein intikhab karna hota, unmein se aik doosrey ki nisbat aasan hota to aap unmein se aasan tareen ka intikhab farmatey, siwaey iske ke wo gunah ho. agar wo gunah hota to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sab logon se badh kar us se door hotey ."
6547,"abu-Usama ne Hisham (bin Urwa) se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko jab bhi 2 kaamon mein intikhab karna hota, unmein se aik doosrey ki nisbat aasan hota to aap unmein se aasan tareen ka intikhab farmatey, siwaey iske ke wo gunah ho. agar wo gunah hota to Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) sab logon se badh kar us se door hotey ."
6548,"abu-Kuraib aur ibne-Numair donon ne Abdullah-bin-Numair se, unhon-ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath unke qaul donon mein se zyada aasan tak riwayat ki aur un donon (abu-Kuraib aur ibne-Numair) ne iske baad wala hissey bayan nahi kya."
6549,"abu-Kuraib aur ibne-Numair donon ne Abdullah-bin-Numair se, unhon-ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath unke qaul donon mein se zyada aasan tak riwayat ki aur un donon (abu-Kuraib aur ibne-Numair) ne iske baad wala hissey bayan nahi kya."
6550,Abu-Bakar-bin-Muhammad-bin-zanjuwia qushairi ne kaha : hamein Abdul-Aala-bin-Hammad narsi ne Hammaad-bin-Salma se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6551,"Saeed-bin-Mansoor aur abu-Rabeea' Zahrani ne kaha : hamein Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Ayub se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se, unhon-ne abu-Asmaa se, unhon-ne Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki. padhi. abu Rabe ne kaha : unhon-ne usey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se marfooan bayan kiya. padhi. aur Saeed ki hadis mein hai : (Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mareez ki iyaadat karne wala wapas aaney tak jannat ke darmyan guzarney wali ravish (raah) par hota hai."
6552,"Hushaim ne hamein Khalid se khabar di, unhon-ne abu-Qilaba se, unhon-ne abu-Asmaa se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aazad karda ghulam Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs kisi mareez ki iyaadat karta hai wo wapas aaney tak musalsal jannat ki aik ravish (raah) par rehta hai."
6553,"Yazeed-bin-zuraia' ne kaha : hamein Khalid ne abu-Qilaba se, unhon-ne abu Asma Rahbi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik musalman jab apne musalman bhai ki iyaadat karta hai to wapas aaney tak musalsal jannat ki aik ravish mein maujood hota hai."
6554,"Yazid-bin-Harun ne kaha : hamein Aasim ahwal ne abu-Qilaba Abdullah-bin-Zaid se khabar sunai, unhon-ne abu-Ash'as se, unhon-ne abu-Asma Rahbi se, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke aazad karda ghulam Hazrat Soban (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne kisi mareez ki iyaadat ki wo musalsal jannat ki ravish mein raha. aap se puchha gaya : ya Rasulullah ! jannat ki ravish kya cheez hai? aap ne farmaya : uske phal jinhein wo chuntaa hai."
6555,Marwan-bin-Muawiya ne Aasim ahwal se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
6556,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din izzat aur jalaal waaley Allah farmaeyga : Adam ke betey ! main bimar hua tu ney meri iyaadat na ki. wo kahega : mere rab ! main kaisey teri iyaadat karta jabke to rabbul-aalameen hai. Allah Taala farmaeyga : kya tumhen malum na tha ke mera falan banda bimar tha? tu ney uski iyaadat na ki. tumhen malum nahi ke agar to uski iyaadat karta to mujhey uske paas paata. aey ibne-Aadam ! maine tujh se khana maanga , tu ney mujhey khana na khilaaya. wo shakhs kahega : aey mere rab ! main tujhey kaisey khana khilata jabke to khud hi sarey jahaanon ko paalne wala hai. Allah Taala farmaeyga : kya tujhey malum nahi ke mere falan bandey ne tujh se khana maanga tha?  tu ney isey khana na khilaaya agar to usko khila deta to tumhen wo (khana) mere paas mil jata. aey ibne-Aadam ! maine tujh se pani maanga tha, tu ney mujhey pani nahi pilaya . wo shakhs kahega : mere rab ! main tujhey kaisey pani pilaataa jabke to khud hi sarey jahaanon ko paalne wala hai. Allah Taala farmaeyga : mere falan bandey ne tujh se pani maanga tha tu ney isey pani na pilaya, agar to usko pani pilaa deta to (aaj) usko mere paas pa leta."
6557,"Usman-bin-abi Sheba aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Waeil se, unhon-ne Masruq se riwayat ki, kaha : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine koi shakhs nahi dekha jisey Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se zyada sakht takleef ka saamnaa karna padaa ho. Usman ki riwayat mein sakht takleef ka saamnaa ke bajaey jiski takleef zyada sakht ho hai."
6558,Shoba aur Sufiyan donon ne Aamash se Jarir ki sanad ke sath usi ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki.
6559,"Usman-bin-abi-Sheba, Zuhair-bin-Harab aur Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim Taimi se, unhon-ne Haaris-bin-Suwed se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin-Masood) (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : main Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua, us waqt aapko bukhar chadh raha tha, maine aapko hath se chhuwa aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! aapko to bahut sakht bukhar chadhaa hua hai. Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan , mujhey itna bukhar chadhtaa hai jitna tum mein se do aadmiyon ko bukhar chadhtaa hai. maine kaha : ye isliye ke aap ke liye dohra ajr hai? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan , (yahi baat hai) phir Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi musalman nahi jisey koi takleef pahunchey, marz ho ya iske alawa koi aur takleef magar Allah uske sabab se uski buraaiyaan (gunah) jhaad deta hai jis tarah darakht apne pattey jhaadta hai. Zuhair ki hadis mein ye alfaz nahi : to maine aapko hath se chhuwa."
6560,"abu-Muawia, Sufiyan, Esa-bin-Yonus aur Yahya-bin-abdul-Malik-bin-abi-ghaniya sab ne Aamash se Jarir ki sanad ke sath , usi ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki aur abu-Muawia ki hadis mein mazeed hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : haan , mujhey us zaat ki qism jiske hath mein meri jaan hai ! poori zamin par koi musalman nahi. padhi."
6561,"Mansoor ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad (bin-Yazeed Nakhai) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : kuchh qureshi naujawaan Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ki khidmat mein hazir huey jabke wo Mina mein thin. wo naujawaan hans rahe they. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne puchha : tum kis wjah se hans rahe ho? unhon-ne kaha : falan shakhs khemey ki rassiyon par gir padaa, qareeb tha ke uski gardan ya aankh jati rehti. is par Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne farmaya : hanso mat, maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya : koi musalman nahi jisey kaanta chubh jaey ya us se badh kar (takleef) ho magar uske liye aik darja likh diya jata hai aur uska aik gunah maaf kar diya jata hai."
6562,"Aamash ne Ibrahim se, unhon-ne Aswad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik momin ko koi kaantaa nahi chubtaa ya us se zyada koi takleef nahi hoti magar Allah Taala is se uska aik darja buland kar deta hai ya uski bina par uska aik gunah mitaa deta hai."
6563,"Muhammad-bin-Bishr ne kaha : hamein Hisham ne apne walid (Urwa) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik momin ko jab bhi koi kaantaa chubtaa hai ya us se badh kar koi takleef hoti hai to Allah Taala iski wjah se uska aik gunah mitaa deta hai."
6564,abu-Muawiya ne hamein Hisham se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki.
6565,"ibne-Shahab ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi bhi museebat nahi jis mein koi musalman mubtala ho magar uski bina par uska koi gunah us se hata diya jata hai, yahan tak ke wo kaantaa bhi jo usey chubtaa hai (aur kisi gunah ka kaffara bin jata hai.)"
6566,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne Yazeed-bin-husaifa se, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalman par koi bhi museebat nahi aati , chahey aik kaantaa hi (chubhaa) ho, magar iski wjah se uski ghaltiyaan maaf kar di jati hain ya isko uski kuchh ghaltiyon ka kaffara bana diya jata hai. Yazeed ko pata nahi ke Urwa ne un donon mein se kon sa jumla bola tha."
6567,"Umra ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : koi bhi museebat nahi jo momin par aati hai, yahan tak ke wo kaantaa bhi jo usey chubtaa hai to Allah iske badley uske liye aik neki likh deta hai ya iski wjah se uski koi ghalati maaf kar di jati hai."
6568,"Ata-bin-Yasar ne Hazrat abu-Saeed aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, donon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : momin ko koi takleef nahi pahunchti , na thakaawat , na bimari , na gham yahan tak ke koi fikr bhi jo usey fikrmand kar de magar iske badley uske gunahon ko mitaa diya jata hai."
6569,"Sufiyan ne Quraish ke aik buzurg ibne-muheesin se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Muhammad-bin-Qais-bin-Makhrima ko Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kartey huey suna, unhon-ne kaha : jab (ye aayat) nazil hui : jo shakhs koi burai karega, iske badley usey saza di jaeygi. ye (baat) musalmanon ke liye sakht khof aur tashwish (pareshani) ka baais bani, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (matlooba mea'yaar ke) qareeb tar pahuncho aur achi tarah seedhey ho jao. har museebat mein, jo kisi musalman ko pahunchti hai, aik kaffara hota hai yahan tak ke thokar jo usey lag jati hai ya kaantaa usey chubh jata hai. Imam Muslim ne kaha : wo (Quraish ke Shekh ibne-muheesin) ahale-Makka mein se Umar-bin-Abdur-Rehman-bin-muheesin hain."
6570,"abu-Zubair ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) (eik Ansari khatun) Hazrat umme-Saaib ya Hazrat umme-Musaiyab (Raziallahu anhu) ke yahan tashrif le gaey, aap ne farmaya : umme-Saaib ya (farmaya :) umme-Musaiyab ! tumhein kya hua? kya tum shiddat se kanp rahi ho? unhon-ne kaha : bukhar hai, Allah Taala usmein barkat na de ! aap ne farmaya : bukhar ko bura na kaho, kyonke ye Adam ki aulad ke gunahon ko is tarah door karta hai jis tarah bhatti lohey ke zang ko door karti hai."
6571,"Ata-bin-abi-Ribah ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : aik din Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) ne mujh se kaha : kya main tumhen ahle-jannat mein se aik aurat na dikhaaun? maine kaha : kyon nahi ! unhon-ne kaha : ye siyah faam (kaale rang ki) aurat hai. ye Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hui aur kaha : Allah ke rasool ! mujh par mirgee ka daurah padta hai jis se (kabhi) mera libaas khul jata hai. aap mere liye Allah se dua kijiye.aap ne farmaya : agar tum chaho to is par sabr karo aur tumharey liye jannat hai aur agar tum chaho to main Allah se dua karta hun ke wo tum ko sihat ata farmaey. us aurat ne kaha : main sabr karun gi, usne kaha : mera libaas khul jata hai, aap Allah se ye dua farma dein ke mera libaas na khuley, to aap ne uske liye dua farmai."
6572,"Marwan-bin-Muhammad-Dimashqi ne kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-Abdul-Azeez ne Rabee-bin-Yazeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Idrees Kholani se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se aik aisi riwayat bayan ki jo aap ne Allah tabarak w taala se bayan ki, Allah Taala ne farmaya : mere bando ! maine zulm karna apne uper haram kiya hai aur tumharey darmyan bhi usey haram qarar diya hai. isliye tum aik doosrey par zulm na karo. mere bando ! tum sab ke sab gumrah ho, siwaey uske jisey main hidayat de dun. isliye mujh se hidayat maango , main tumhen hidayat doonga. mere bando ! tum sab ke sab bhookey ho, siwaey uske jisey main khilaaun , isliye mujh se khana maango , main tumhen khilaaun ga. mere bando ! tum sab ke sab nangey ho, siwaey uske jisey main libaas pahnaaoon, lihaza mujh se libaas maango, main tumhen libaas pahnaaoon ga. mere bando ! tum din raat gunah kartey ho aur main hi sab ke sab gunah maaf karta hun, so mujh se maghfirat maango main tumharey gunah maaf karunga. mere bando ! tum kabhi mujhey nuqsan pahunchaney ki taqat nahi rakho gey ke mujhey nuqsan pahuncha sako, na kabhi mujhey fayda pahunchaney ke qaabil hon gey ke mujhey fayda pahuncha sako. mere bando ! agar tumharey pahley waley aur tumharey baad waley aur tumharey insan aur tumharey 'jinn' sab mil kar tum mein se aik intihai muttaqi insan ke dil ke mutabiq ho jayen to is se meri badhshahat mein koi izafa nahi ho sakta. mere bando ! agar tumharey pahley waley aur tumharey baad waley aur tumharey insan aur tumharey 'jinn' sab mil kar tum mein se sabse faajir (badkar) aadmi ke dil ke mutabiq ho jayen to us se meri badhshahat mein koi kami nahi hogi. mere bando ! agar tumharey pahley aur tumharey pichhley aur tumharey insan aur tumharey 'jinn' sab mil kar aik khuley maidan mein khadey ho jayen aur mujh se maangein aur main har aik ko uski mangi hui cheez ata kar dun to us se jo mere paas hai, usmein itna bhi kam nahi hoga jo us sui se (kam hoga) jo samandar mein dali (aur nikali) jaey. Saeed ne kaha : abu-Idrees Kholani jab ye hadis bayan kartey to apne ghutnon ke bal baith jatey."
6573,"Abu-Bakar-bin-Ishaq ne kaha : hamein abu-Mus'hir ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Saeed-bin-Abdul-Azeez ne isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, albatta Marwan ki hadis zyada mukammal hai."
6574,"Abu-Ishaq ne kaha : hamein ye hadis Bishr ke do beton Hasan aur Husain ne aur Muhammad-bin-Yahyaa ne bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Mus'hir ne hadis bayan ki, phir poori lambi hadis bayan ki."
6575,"abu-Asmaa ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala ne farmaya : maine apne uper aur apne bandon par zulm ko haram kar diya hai, lihaza aik doosrey par zulm na karo aur (iske baad) usi (pichhli hadis ki) tarah hadis bayan ki aur abu-Idrees ( Kholani ( ki hadis jo ham ne (pahley) bayan ki hai us se zyada mukammal hai."
6576,"Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zulm se bacho, kyonke zulm qiyamat ke din (dilon par chhaaney wali) zulmatein (andhera) hongi . kanjoosii aur hawas se bacho , kyonke tum se pahley logon ko kanjoosii aur hawas ne halaak kar diya. usi ne unko uksaya to unhon-ne apne (eik doosrey ke) khoon bahaaey aur apni hurmat wali chizon ko halal kar liya."
6577,"Abdullah-bin-Dinar ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zulm qiyamat ke din kai zulmatein (taareekiyaan,andherey) hongi ."
6578,"Salim ne apne walid se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalman doosrey musalman ka bhai hai, na is par zulm karta hai, na usey (zaalimon ke) supurd karta hai. jo shakhs apne bhai ki haajat poori karne mein laga hota hai, Allah Taala uski haajat rawaai farmata hai. jo kisi musalman se uski aik takleef door karta hai, Allah Taala us se qiyamat ki takleefon mein se aik takleef door karta hai. jo shakhs kisi musalman ki parda poshi karta hai, Allah Taala qiyamat ke din us (ke aibon) ki parda poshi farmaeyga."
6579,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum jantey ho ke muflis kon hai? sahaba ne kaha : hamarey nazdeek muflis wo shakhs hai jiske paas na dirham ho, na koi saazo-saamaan. aap ne farmaya : meri ummat ka muflis wo shakhs hai jo qiyamat ke din namaz, roza aur zakat lekar aayega aur is tarah aayega ke (duniya mein) usko gali di hogi, is par bohtan lagaya hoga, uska maal khaya hoga, uska khoon bahaya hoga aur usko maara hoga, to uski nekiyon mein se isko bhi diya jaeyga aur usko bhi diya jaeyga aur agar is par jo zimma hai uski adaaeygi se pahley uski saari nekiyan khatm ho jaeyngi to uske gunahon ko lekar is par daala jaeyga, phir usko jahannam mein phenk diya jaeyga."
6580,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : qiyamat ke din tum sab haqdaaron ke huquq unko ada karogey, yahan tak ke us bakri ka badla bhi jiske seeng tod diye gaey hongey, seengon wali bakri se pura pooraa liya jaeyga"
6581,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Allah Taala zaalim ko mohlat de deta hai aur jab usko pakad leta hai to phir janey nahi deta. phir aap ne (ye aayat) padhi : aur jab wo zulm karne wali bastiyon ko apni giraft mein leta hai to aap ke rab ki giraft aisi hi hoti hai (ke koi bach nahi sakta. ( be-shak uski giraft sakht dardnak hai."
6582,"abu-Zubair ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, kaha : 2 ladkey aapas mein lad padey , aik ladka muhajireen mein se tha aur doosra ladka Ansar mein se. muhajir ne pukar kar awaz di : aey muhajireen ! aur Ansari ne pukar kar awaz di : aey Ansar ! to ( achcha ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) bahar tashrif ley aaey aur farmaya : ye kya zamana jahiliyat ki si cheekh w pukar hai? unhon-ne kaha : nahi, Allah ke rasool! bas ye 2 ladkey aapas mein lad padey hain aur aik ne doosrey ki peeth par zarb lagai hai, aap ne farmaya : koi ( badi ( baat nahi, aur har insan ko apne bhai ki, chahe wo zaalim ho ya mazloom , madad karni chahiye, agar iska bhai zaalim ho to usey ( zulm se) rokey , yahi uski madad hai, aur agar mazloom ho to uski madad kare."
6583,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne kaha : Amr (bin Dinar ( ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : ham aik ghazwey ( jang muraisia) main Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath they, wahan aik muhajir ne aik Ansari ki peeth par zarb lagai , Ansari ne kaha : aey Ansar ! ( aao, madad karo (aur muhajir ne kaha : aey muhaajiro ! ( aao, madad karo. ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ye kya zamana jahiliyat ki tarah ki cheekh w pukar hai? unhon-ne kaha : ya Rasulullah ! aik muhajir shakhs ne aik Ansari ki peeth par maara hai, aap ne farmaya : (jab ye itna chhota sa mamla hai to jaahili daur ki si) us (cheekh w pukar ( ko chhodo . ye aik kareeh aur badbudar baat hai. Abdullah-bin Ubai ne ye baat suni to kehney laga : (achchha!) unhon-ne (aisa) kya hai, Allah ki qism ! jab ham Madina pahunchengey to ham mein se izzat wala usey, jo zillat wala hai, wahan se nikal bahar karega . Hazrat umr (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : mujhey chhodiye , main us munafiq ki gardan udaata hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : usey rehney do, kahin log ye na kahin ke Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) apne hi sathiyon ko qatl kar rahe hain."
6584,"Ishaq-bin-Ibrahim, Ishaq-bin-Mansur aur Muhammad-bin Raafe ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. ibne-Raafe ne kaha : hamein hadis bayan ki jabke doosrey donon ne kaha : khabar di. padhi. Abdur-Razzaq ne kaha : hamein Mamar ne Ayub se khabar di, unhon-ne Amr-bin-Dinar se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik muhajir ne aik Ansari ki peeth par maara, wo Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur aap se badla dilwaaey ki darkhaast ki, ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne zaroori kaarrwaai ke baad) logon se kaha is ( cheekh w pukar aur fasaad angezii ( ko chhod do, ye aik kareeh aur badbudar ( harkat ( hai. ibne- Mansoor ne apni riwayat mein Amr se riwayat kartey huey sarahat ki ke Amr ne kaha : maine Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna."
6585,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik musalman doosrey musalman ke liye aik Imaarat ki tarah hai, jiski aik (ent) dusri (ent) ko mazbut karti hai."
6586,"Zakariya ne hamein Shabi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalmanon ki aik doosrey se mohabbat , aik doosrey ke sath rehem dilli aur aik doosrey ki taraf iltifaat w taawun ki misal aik jism ki tarah hai, jab iske aik uzu (khaas ang) ko takleef hoti hai to baqi Sara jism bedaari aur bukhar ke zariey se (sab aaza ko aik-doosrey ke sath mila kar) uska sath deta hai."
6587,"Mutarrif ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ( guzishta hadis) ki tarah riwayat ki."
6588,"Wakee ne Aamash se, unhon-ne Shabi se, unhon-ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalman ( aapasii ( aik hi insan ki tarah hain, agar uske sar mein takleef ho to bukhar aur be khuwaabi ke zariey se baqi Sara jism iska sath deta hai."
6589,"khaisma (bin Abdur-Rehman ( ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : musalman (aapas mein) aik insan ki tarah hain, agar uski aankh mein takleef ho to sarey jism ko takleef hoti hai aur agar sar mein takleef ho to uske sarey jism ko takleef hoti hai."
6590,Shabi ne Hazrat Noman-bin-Bashir (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se isi tarah riwayat ki.
6591,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik doosrey ko bura bhala kehney waley jo kuchh bhi kehtey hain, iska wabaal pahal karne waley par hai jab tak mazloom had se tajaawuz na kare."
6592,Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sadqey ne maal mein kabhi koi kami nahi ki aur maaf karne se Allah Taala bandey ko izzat hi mein badhata hai aur koi shakhs ( sirf aur sirf ( Allah ki khaatir tawaazeh ( inkisaar ( ikhtiyar nahi karta magar Allah Taala iska maqam buland kar deta hai.
6593,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya tum jantey ho ke gheebat kya hai? unhon (sahaba) ne kaha : Allah aur uska rasool khub jaanney waley hain. aap ne farmaya : apne bhai ka is tarah tazkira karna jo usey na-pasand ho. kaha gaya : aap ye dekhiye ke agar mere bhai mein wo baat waqei maujood ho jo main kehta hun (to? (aap ne farmaya : jo kuchh tum kehtey ho, agar usmein maujood hai to tum ne uski gheebat ki, agar usmein wo ( aib ( maujood nahi to tum ne is par bohtan lagaya hai."
6594,"Rauh ( bin-Qasim ( ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid ( Abu-Saleh ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : Allah Taala duniya mein jis shakhs ki parda-poshi karta hai, qiyamat ke din bhi uska parda rakhega ."
6595,"Wuhaib ne kaha : hamein Suhel ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : duniya mein koi banda kisi (doosrey ( bandey ka aib nahi chhipaata magar qiyamat ke roz Allah Taala uske aib chipa lega."
6596,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne ibne-Munkadir se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Urwa-bin-Zubair ko ye kehtey huey suna ke mujhey Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne hadis bayan ki ke aik shakhs ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mulaqat ki ijazat talab ki, aap ne farmaya : usko ijazat de do, ye yaqinan apne qabeeley ka bura fard hai, ya farmaya : qabeeley ka bura mard hai. jab wo shakhs andar aaya to aap ne uske sath narmi se guftgu ki. Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap ne iske barey mein wo farmaya jo farmaya tha, phir aap ne iske sath narmi se baat ki? aap ne farmaya : Aaisha ! qiyamat ke din Allah Taala ke nazdeek rutbey ke eitibaar se sabse bura shakhs wo hoga jis se log uski bad-zabaani se bchney ke liye door rahen ya usko chhod dein."
6597,"Mamar ne ibne-Munkadir se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana riwayat bayan ki, magar unhon-ne kaha : ye qaum ka badtareen fard hai aur ye gharaaney ka ( badtareen ( fard hai."
6598,"Mansoor ne Tameem bin Salma se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin Hilal se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jis shakhs ko narm khui se mahroom kar diya jaey, wo bhalai se mahroom kar diya jata hai."
6599,"Aamash ne Tameem bin Salma se, unhon-ne Abdur-Rehman bin Hilal absa se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jarir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo kehtey hain : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farma rahe they : jo shakhs narm khui se mehroom kar diya jaey wo bhalai se mahroom kar diya jata hai."
6600,"Muhammad-bin Ismail ne Abdur-Rehman bin Hilal se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Jareer-bin-Abdullaah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jo shakhs narm mizaaji se mehroom hua wo bhalai se mehroom hua, ya jo shakhs narm mizaaji se mahroom kar diya jata hai wo bhalai se mahroom kar diya jata hai."
6601,"Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aaisha! Allah Taala narmi karne wala hai aur narmi ko pasand farmata hai aur narmi ki bina par wo kuchh ata farmata hai jo kaduwey mizaaj ki bina par ata nahi farmata, wo uske ilawa kisi bhi aur baat par itna ata nahi farmata."
6602,"Muaz Anbari ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Miqdaam-bin-Shureh bin Hani se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki ahliya Hazrat Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : narmi jis cheez mein bhi hoti hai usko zeenat bakhsh deti hai aur jis cheez se bhi narmi nikal di jati hai usey bad-soorat kar deti hai."
6603,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Miqdaam-bin-Shureh bin Hani ko isi sanad se ( hadis bayan kartey huey) suna aur unhon-ne hadis mein mazeed bayan kya : Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) aik aisey oont par Sawar huin jis mein abhi sarkashi thi to Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) usey ghumaaney lagin, is par Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Aaisha ! narmi se kaam lo. iske baad usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah bayan kya."
6604,"Ismail bin Ibrahim ne kaha : hamein Ayub ne abu-Qilaba se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Mohlab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Imran-bin-Husain (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik baar Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aik safar mein they aur aik Ansari aurat ontni par Sawar thi ke achcha wo ontni bechain hui, us aurat ne is par laanat ki to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ye baat sun li, aap ne farmaya is ( ontni ( par jo kuchh maujood hai wo hata lo aur usko chhodo kyonke wo maloon ontni hai. Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain ke jaisey mein ab bhi dekh raha hun ke wo ontni logon ke darmyan chal rahi hai, koi us se chhed-chhad nahi karta."
6605,"Hammad-bin-Zaid aur) abdul-wahaab ( Saqafi ne Ayub se Ismail ki sanad ke sath usi ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar Hammad ki hadis mein hai : Hazrat Imran (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : jaisey ab bhi main usko dekh raha hun, wo khaakastri rang ki aik ontni hai. aur Saqafi ki hadis mein hai ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : is par jo kuchh hai utaar lo, uski peeth nangi kar do kyonke wo aik maloon ontni hai."
6606,"Yazeed bin Zure ne kaha : hamein Taimi ne abu-Usman se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik baandi aik ontni par Sawar thi jis par logon ka kuchh saman bhi lada hua tha, achcha us ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko dekha, us waqt pahaad (ke darrey ne) guzarney walon ka rasta tang kar diya tha. us baandi ne ( ontni ko tez karne ke liye zor se) kaha : chal ( tez chalo taake Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke qareeb pahunch jayen, jab wo ontni tez na hui to kehney lagi : (aey Allah ! is par laanat bhej (Hazrat abu-Barza Aslami (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : wo ontni jis par laanat ho hamarey sath ( Sharike-safar ( na ho."
6607,"Motamir bin Sulaiman aur Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Sulaiman Taimi se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, Motamir ki hadis mein mazeed ye hai (ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( nahi, Allah ki qism ! aisi ontni hamarey sath na rahe jis par Allah ki laanat ho. ya aap ne jin alfaz mein farmaya,"
6608,"Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne mujhey khabar di, kaha : Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman se riwayat hai, unhon-ne apne walid se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik siddeeq ke shaayaan shaan nahi ke wo zyada laanat karne wala ho."
6609,Muhammad-bin-Jafar ne Alaa bin Abdur-Rehman se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
6610,"Hafs-bin-Maisra ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se riwayat ki ke Abdul-Malik bin Marwan ne Hazrat Umme- Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ko apni taraf se ghar ka kuchh umda saman bheja , phir aisa hua ke aik raat ko Abdul-Malik utha , us ne apne khaadim ko awaz di, ghaaliban us ne der laga di to Abdul-Malik ne is par laanat ki, jab us ( Abdul-Malik ( ne subah ki to Hazrat Umme- Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine raat ko suna ke jis waqt tum ne apne khaadim ko bulaya tha to tum ne is par laanat ki thi, phir wo kehney lagein : maine Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna tha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : zyada laanat karne waley qiyamat ke din na shafaat karne waley hongey, na gawah banengey ."
6611,Mamar ne Zaid-bin-Aslam se isi sanad se Hafs-bin-Maisra ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki.
6612,"Hisham bin Sad ne Zaid-bin-Aslam aur abu-Hazim se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Umme- Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Darda (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : bila shubah zyada laanat karne waley qiyamat ke roz na shahadat dene waley hongey aur na shafaat karne waley ."
6613,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : Allah ke rasool! mushrekeen ke khilaf dua kijiye. aap ne farmaya : mujhey laanat karne wala bana kar nahi bheja gaya, mujhey to rehmat bana kar bheja gaya hai."
6614,"Jarir ne Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Zuhaa se, unhon-ne Masruq se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas 2 log aaey, mujhey malum nahi kis mamley mein unhon-ne aap se guftgu ki aur aapko naraz kar diya, aap ne un par laanat ki aur un donon ko bura kaha, jab wo nikal kar chaley gaey to maine kaha : koi shakhs bhi jisey koi khair mili ho (wo ( un donon ko nahi mili . aap ne farmaya : wo kaisey? kaha : maine kaha : aap ne unko laanat ki aur bura kaha, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tumhen ilm nahi hai maine apne rab se kya shart ki hui hai? maine kaha hai : aey Allah ! main sirf insan hun, lihaza main jis musalman ko laanat karun ya bura kahun to us (laanat aur bura bhala kehney ( ko uske liye gunahon se pakeezgi aur husoole ajr ka zaria bana de."
6615,"abu-Muawia aur Esa-bin-Yonus ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath Jarir ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, aur Esa (bin Yunus ( ki hadis mein kaha : wo donon Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se alehadgi mein miley to aap ne unhein bura bhala kaha, un donon par laanat bheji aur unko nikal diya."
6616,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Abu-Saleh se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aey Allah ! main sirf aik insan hun, isliye main jis musalman ko bura bhala kahun ya is par laanat karun ya usko kode maarun to usey us ke liye pakeezgi (ka zaria) aur rehmat bana de."
6617,"Abdullah-bin-Numair ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Abu-Sufiyan se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi hadis ki tarah riwayat ki magar usmein pakeezgi aur ajr ke alfaz hain."
6618,"abu-Muawia aur Esa-bin-Yonus ne Aamash se Abdullah-bin-Numair ki sanad ke sath usi ki hadis ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar Esa ki riwayat mein Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis mein bana de aur ajr ke lafz hain aur Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadis main aur bana de aur rehmat ke lafz hain."
6619,"Mughira bin Abdur-Rehman hazami ne hamein abu-Zinaad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne ( dua kartey huey) farmaya : aey Allah! main tujh se ahad leta hun jis main to mere sath hargiz khilaf warzi nahi farmaeyga ke main aik insan hi hun, main jis kisi momin ko takleef pahunchaaun, usey bura bhala kahun, is par laanat karun usey kode maarun to un tamam baton ko qiyamat ke din uske liye rehmat, pakeezgi aur aisi qurbat bana de jiske zariey se to usey apna qurb ata farmaey."
6620,"abu-Zinad ne hamein isi sanad ke sath ye riwayat bayan ki, albatta unhon-ne ( جلدة ( kaha, abu-Zinad ne kaha : ye Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki zaban hai. (Quraish ki zaban mein) ye lafz ( جلدتہ ( hi hai. ( mana aik hi hai, yani jisey main kode maarun.)"
6621,"Ayub ne Abdur-Rehman Aaraj se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6622,"nasriyon ke aazad karda ghulam Salim ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko kehtey huey suna, keh rahe they ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ( dua kartey huey) farma rahe they : aey Allah ! Muhammad aik insan hi hai, jis tarah aik insan ko ghussa aata hai, usey bhi ghussa aata hai aur main terey huzoor aik wada leta hun jis main to mere sath hargiz khilaf warzi nahi farmaeyga ke jis momin ko bhi maine takleef pahunchai , usey bura-bhala kaha ya kode se maara to us sab kuchh ko uske liye gunahon ka kaffara bana dena aur aisi qurbat mein badal dena jiske zariey se qiyamat ke din to usey apna qurb ata farmaai ."
6623,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se khabar di ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ( dua kartey huey) farma rahe they : aey Allah ! main jis banda momin ko bura bhala kahun to uske liye usey qiyamat ke din apni qurbat mein badal dena."
6624,"ibne-Shahab ke bhatijey ne apne chacha se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ( dua kartey huey) farma rahe they : aey Allah ! maine terey huzoor pukhta ahad liya hai jis main to mere sath hargiz khilaf warzi nahi farmaeyga ke koi bhi momin jisey maine takleef pahunchai ho ya usey bura bhala kaha ho ya usey kode se maara ho, usey to qiyamat ke din uske liye ( gunahon ka ( kaffara bana dena."
6625,"Hajjaj-bin Muhammad ne kaha : ibne-Juraij ne kaha : mujhey abu-Zubair ne bataya , unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se ye suna, aap farmatey they : main aik insan hi hun aur maine apne rab azz-w-jall se ye ahad liya hai ke main musalmanon mein se jis bandey ko bura-bhala karun to ye sab kuchh uske liye pakeezgi aur ajr (ka sabab) bin jaey."
6626,Rooh aur abu-Aasim donon ne hamein ibne-Juraij se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6627,"Zuhair-bin-Harab aur abu-Man Raqashi ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. aur alfaz Zuhair ke hain. padhi. donon ne kaha : hamein Umar-bin Yunus ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Ikrima bin Ammar ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Ishaq bin abi Talha ne hadis sunai, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne bayan kya ke Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas aik yateem ladki thi aur yahi ( Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu)) Umme- Anas bhi kahlaati thin, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne usko dekha to farmaya : to wahi ladki hai, to badi ho gaee hai ! teri umr (is tezi se) badi na ho wo ladki roti hui wapas Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ke paas gaee, Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne puchha : beti ! tujhey kya hua? usne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mere khilaf dua farma di hai ke meri umr zyada na ho, ab meri umr kisi sura zyada na hogi, ya kaha : ab mera zamana hargiz zyada nahi hoga, Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) jaldi se dupatta lapetey huey niklin, yahan tak ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas hazir huin , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne unse puchha : Umme-Sulaim ! kya baat hai? Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ke Nabi ! kya aap ne meri (pali hui) yateem ladki ke khilaf dua ki hai? aap ne puchha : ye kya baat hai? Hazrat Umme-Sulaim (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : wo kehti hai : aap ne dua farmai hai ke uski umr zyada na ho, aur uska zamana lamba na ho, (Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) hansey , phir farmaya : Umme-Sulaim ! kya tumhen malum nahi ke maine apne rab se pukhta ahad liya hai, maine kaha : main aik insan hi hun, jis tarah aik insan khush hota hai, main bhi khush hota hun aur jis tarah insan naraz hotey hain mein bhi naraz hota hun. to meri ummat mein se koi bhi aadmi jiske khilaf maine dua ki aur wo iska mustahiq na tha to us dua ko qiyamat ke din uske liye pakeezgi, gunahon se safaai aur aisi qurbat bana de jiske zariey se to usey apne qareeb farma ley. abu Ma'n (معن) ne kaha : hadis mein teenon jagah ( yateema ke bajaey) tasgheer ke sath ( يتيمة ( ) chhoti si yateem bachchi ka lafz) hai."
6628,"Muhammad-bin-Musanna Anzi aur ibne-Bashar ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz ibne-Musanna ke hain. padhi. donon ne kaha : hamein Umayya bin Khalid ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne abu-Hamza qassab se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : main ladkon ke sath khel raha tha ke achcha Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif ley aaey, mein darwazey ke peechhey chhup gaya, kaha : aap aaey aur mere donon shaanon ke darmyan apne khuley hath se halki si zarb lagai (maqsood piyaar ka izhar tha) aur farmaya : jao, mere liye Muawiya ko bula laao. maine aap se aa kar kaha : wo khana kha rahe hain. aap ne dobara mujh se farmaya : jao, Muawiya ko bula laao. maine phir aa kar kaha : wo khana kha rahe hain, to aap ne farmaya : Allah iska pet na bharey ."
6629,"Nazar-bin-Shumail ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein abu-Hamza ne khabar di ke maine Hazrat Ibne-Abbas (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, kehtey they : main bachchon ke sath khel raha tha, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) tashrif ley aaey to main aap se chhup gaya. aagey usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah bayan kya."
6630,Aaraj ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : badtareen insanon mein se do-rukha shakhs ( bhi) hota hai. wo un logon se aik chehrey ke sath milta hai aur un logon se doosrey chehrey ke sath milta hai.
6631,"Irak bin Malik ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko farmatey huey suna : logon mein se badtareen shakhs 2 chehron wala hota hai, jo un logon ke paas aik chehrey se aata hai aur un logon ke paas doosrey chehrey se aata hai."
6632,"Saeed-bin-Musaiyab aur Abu-Zaraa ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum logon mein se badtareen shakhs usey paogey jiske 2 chehrey hain, unke paas aik chehra lekar aata hai aur unke paas doosra chehra lekar aata hai."
6633,"Yunus ne ibne-Shahab se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf ne khabar di ke unki walida Hazrat Umme-Kulsum binte- Aqba bin abi mueet (Raziallahu anhu) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke sath bait karne wali un khawaateen mein se thin jinhoney sabse pahley hijrat ki. unhon-ne usey (apne betey ko) khabar di ke unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna aap farma rahe they : wo shakhs jhoota nahi jo logon mein suleh kiraaey aur achi baat kahey aur achi baat pahunchaaey . ibne-Shahab ne kaha : log jo jhooti baatein kartey hain, maine unmein se teen ke siwa kisi baat ke barey mein nahi suna ke unki ijazat di gaee hai : jang aur jihad mein, logon ke darmyan suleh karaaney ke liye aur khawind ka apni biwi se ( usey razi karne ki) baat aur aurat ki apne khawind se ( usey razi karne ke liye) baat ."
6634,"Saleh ne kaha : hamein Muhammad-bin Muslim-bin Ubaidullah bin-Abdullah-bin Shahab ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki, magar Saleh ki hadis mein hai : aur) Umme-Kulsum binte- Aqba (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine aap se nahi suna ke log jo baatein kartey hain aap ne unmein se teen ke siwa kisi baat ki ijazat di ho. ( aagey ( usi ki tarah jis tarah Yunus ne ibne-Shahab ka qaul bataya hai."
6635,Mamar ne hamein Zohri se isi sanad ke sath aap ke us farman tak khabar di : aur achi baat pahunchai aur uske baad ka hissa bayan nahi kya.
6636,"Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : kya main tum ko ye na bataaun ke badtareen haram kya hai? ye chughli hai jo logon ki zaban par rawaan ho jati hai. aur Muhammad (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : insan sach boltaa rehta hai yahan tak ke) Allah Taala ke yahan ( wo siddeeq likh diya jata hai aur jhoot boltaa rehta hai yahan tak ke usko kazzaab likh diya jata hai."
6637,"Jarir ne Mansoor se, unhon-ne abu-Waeil (Shaqeeq) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sach neki aur achai ke rastey par ley jata hai aur neki jannat ki taraf ley jati hai, aik aadmi sach boltaa rehta hai yahan tak ke wo Allah ke yahan siddeeq likh diya jata hai aur jhoot fisq w fujoor ki taraf ley jata hai aur fisq w fujoor (jahannam ki) aag ki taraf ley jata hai aur aik aadmi jhoot boltaa rehta hai, yahan tak ke Allah Taala ke nazdeek usey kazzaab likh diya jata hai."
6638,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba aur Hannaad bin sarii ne kaha : hamein abu-Ahwas ne Mansoor se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne abu-Waail se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : sach neki hai aur neki jannat ki taraf rehnumai karti hai aur banda poori koshish se sach hi ka irada karta rehta hai yahan tak ke wo Allah Taala ke nazdeek siddeeq likh diya jata hai aur jhoot kaj rawii hai aur kaj rawi jahannam ki taraf ley jati hai aur banda jhoot bolney ka irada karta rehta hai yahan tak ke usey jhoota likh diya jata hai. ibne-Abi-Sheba ki riwayat main ( Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya ke bajaey) Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai ke alfaz hain."
6639,"abu-Muawia aur Wakee ne kaha : hamein Aamash ne Shaqiq ( abu-Waeil ( se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum sachchey par qaaim raho kyonke sachchey neki ke rastey par chalaataa hai aur neki jannat ke rastey par chalaati hai. insan musalsal sach boltaa rehta hai aur koshish se sach par qaaim rehta hai, yahan tak ke wo Allah ke yahan sachcha likh liya jata hai aur jhoot se door raho kyonke jhoot kaj rawi ke rastey par chalaataa hai aur kaj rawi aag ki taraf ley jati hai, insan musalsal jhoot boltaa rehta hai aur jhoot ka irada karta rehta hai yahan tak ke Allah Taala ke nazdeek usey jhoota likh liya jata hai."
6640,"ibne-Mus-hir aur Esa-bin-Yonus donon ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath khabar di, unhon-ne Esa ki riwayat mein : sachchey ka irada karta rehta hai aur jhoot ka irada karta rehta hai ke alfaz zikr nahi kiye aur ibne-Mus-hir ki riwayat main ( Allah ke nazdeek ke bajaey) yahan tak ke Allah usko likh leta hai ke alfaz hain."
6641,"Jarir ne hamein Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Ibrahim Taimi se, unhon-ne Haris bin Suwed se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah-bin-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum log apne khayal mein raqoob kisey shumaar kartey ho? ham ne kaha : jis shakhs ke bachchey paida na hotey hun. aap ne farmaya : ye raqoob nahi hai, balke raqoob wo shakhs hai jisne ( aakhirat mein) kisi bachchey ko aagey na bheja ho. aap ne farmaya : tum apne khayal mein pahlwaan kisey samajhtey ho? ham ne kaha : jis ko log pachhaad na sakein . aap ne farmaya : pahlwaan wo nahi hai, balke pahlwaan to wo shakhs hai jo ghussey ke waqt khud par qaabu rakhta hai."
6642,abu-Muawia aur Esa-bin-Yonus ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath usi ke ham mana riwayat ki.
6643,Saeed-bin-Musaiyab ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : (koi shakhs) pachhaad deney se taaqatwar nahi hota. taaqatwar ( mazbut ( wo hai jo ghussey ke waqt khud ko qaabu mein rakhta hai.
6644,"Zubaidi ne Zohri se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman ne bataya ke Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap farmatey they : pachhaad deney se koi shakhs taaqatwar nahi hota. sahaba ne puchha : Allah ke rasool! phir taqatwar kon hai? aap ne farmaya : jo ghussey ke waqt khud ko qaabu mein rakhta hai."
6645,"Mamar aur Shuaib donon ne Zohri se khabar di, unhon-ne Humaid bin Abdur-Rehman-bin-Auf se, unhon-ne Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
6646,"Yahya-bin-Yahya aur Muhammad-bin Alaa ne kaha : hamein abu-Muawia ne Aamash se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Adi-bin-Sabit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Sulaiman-bin Surad (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : 2 aadmiyon ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney aapas mein gaalam galoch kya, un 2 mein se aik ki aankhen surkh ho gain aur gardan ki ragein phool gaen to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : mujhey aik aisa kalima malum hai ke agar ye shakhs usey keh de to wo (ghussey ki) jis kaifiyat mein khud ko pa raha hai wo jati rahegi, (wo kalima hai) : ( اعوذبالله من الشيطان الرجيم (us aadmi ne kaha : kya aap mujh par junoon taari dekhtey hain? ibne- Alaa ki riwayat main ( sirf (aur kya aap dekhtey hain ke alfaz hain aur unhon-ne aadmi ka tazkira nahi kya."
6647,"abu-Usama ne kaha : maine Aamash se suna, wo keh rahe they : maine Adii-bin Sabit se suna, wo keh rahe they ke hamein Sulaiman-bin Surad (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke samney 2 aadmiyon ne aapas mein gaalam galoch kya. unmein se aik ko ghussa chadhna shuru ho gaya aur iska chehra surkh honey laga. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne uski taraf nazar ki aur farmaya : mujhey aik kalimey : ( اعوذبالله من الشيطان الرجيم (ka pata hai. agar ye shakhs wo ( kalima ( keh de to us se ye ( ghussa ( jata rahega. Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se (ye baat ( sunney walon mein se aik aadmi uth kar us shakhs ki taraf gaya aur kaha : tumhen pata hai ke abhi abhii Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne kya farmaya hai? aap ne farmaya hai : mujhey aik aisey kalimey : ( اعوذبالله من الشيطان الرجيم (ka pata hai. agar ye ( shakhs) wo ( kalima ( keh de to us se ye kaifiyat jati rahegi . us shakhs ne kaha : kya tum ye samajh rahe ho ke main junoon ka shikar ho gaya hun?"
6648,Hafs bin Ghiyas ne Aamash se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki.
6649,"Yunus bin-Muhammad ne Hammaad-bin-Salma se, unhon-ne Sabit se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Allah Taala ne jannat mein Hazrat Adam (Alaihissalam) ki sura bana li to jab tak chaha un (ke jasad) ko wahan rakha. iblees iske ird-gird ghoom kar dekhney laga ke wo kaisa hai. jab usne dekha ke wo (jism) andar se khokhla hai to usne jaan liya ke usey is tarah paida kya gaya ke ye khud par qaabu nahi rakh sakta."
6650,Behaz ne kaha : hamein Hammad ne isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6651,"Mughira hazrami ne hamein abu-Zinaad se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Aaraj se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs apne ( musalman ( bhai se ladey to chehrey ( par maarney ( se ijtinab kare."
6652,hamein Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne abu-Zinad se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha : jab tum mein se koi (doosrey ko) maarey.
6653,Suhel ke walid ( Abu-Saleh ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs apne bhai se ladey to chehrey ( par maarney ( se bachey.
6654,"Shoba ne hamein Qatada se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Ayub se suna, Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they. unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs apne bhai se ladey to iske chehrey par tamaancha na maarey ."
6655,"Nasar bin Ali jahazmi ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Musanna (bin Saeed) ne hadis bayan ki, neez mujhey Muhammad-bin-Hatim ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : hamein Abdur-Rehman-bin-Mehdi ne Musanna bin Saeed se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Abu-Ayub se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya aur ibne-abi Hatim ki hadis mein hai : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat hai, aap ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi apne bhai se ladey to chehrey se ijtinab karey kyonke Allah ne Adam ko uski sura par banaya hai."
6656,"Hammam ne kaha : hamein Qatada ne Abu-Ayub Yahya bin Malik muraaghi se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs apne bhai se ladey to chehrey ( par maarney ( se bachey."
6657,"Hafs bin Ghiyas ne Hisham-bin-Urwa se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Hisham bin Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Sham (Syria) mein unka kuchh logon ke qareeb se guzra hua jinko dhoop mein khada kya gaya tha aur unke saron par Zaitoon ka tel daala gaya tha, unhon-ne puchha : ye kya ho raha hai? bataya gaya : unko khiraaj (na dene) ki wjah se saza di ja rahi hai to (Hazrat Hisham bin Hakeem-bin-Hizaam (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se suna, aap ne farmaya : Allah Taala un logon ko azab mein mubtala karega, jo duniya mein logon ko azab detey hain."
6658,"abu-Usama ne Hisham se, unhon-ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Hazrat Hisham bin Hakeem-bin-Hizam (Raziallahu anhu) Sham (Syria) ke chand nabtiyon (Saami qaum / zameendaar logon (ke qareeb se guzrey , unhein dhoop mein khada kya gaya tha, unhon-ne puchha : unka mamla kya hai? logon ne bataya : unhein jiziye (ki adaaeygi ke mamley) mein mahboos kya gaya hai, to Hazrat Hisham (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main gawahi deta hun ke maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : Allah Taala un logon ko azab dega jo duniya mein logon ko azab detey hain."
6659,"Wakee, abu-Muawia aur Jarir sab ne Hisham se isi sanad ke sath hadis bayan ki, aur Jarir ki hadis mein mazeed ye hai, kaha : aur Palestine par un dinon un logon ka ameer Umer bin Sad ( Ansari ( tha to wo ( Hisham (Raziallahu anhu)) unke paas gaey, unko hadis sunai to unhon-ne unke barey mein hukm diya, chunanche unko chhod diya gaya."
6660,"ibne-Shahab ne Urwa-bin-Zubair se riwayat ki ke Hazrat Hisham bin-Hakim (Raziallahu anhu) ne aik shakhs ko dekha, wo teiswin ka aamil tha. us ne nabtiyon mein se kuchh logon ko jiziye ki adaaeygi ke silsiley mein dhoop mein khada kya hua tha to unhon-ne puchha : ye kya hai? maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : bila shubah Allah Taala un logon ko mubtlaaey azab karega jo duniya mein logon ko azab mein mubtala kartey hain."
6661,"Sufiyan-bin-Uena ne Amr (bin Dinar ( se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se suna, wo keh rahe they : aik shakhs chand teer lekar masjid mein se guzra to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : un teeron ko unki nokon (ki taraf se) pakdo ."
6662,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne Amr-bin-Dinar se, unhon-ne Hazrat Jabir-bin-Abdullah (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik shakhs chand teer lekar masjid mein se guzra , us ne unke paikaan khol rakhey they, aap ne hukm diya ke wo unhein paikaanon ( aagey waley lohey ke naukdaar hisson ( ki taraf se pakdey taake wo kisi musalman ko kharaash na laga dein."
6663,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Rumeh ne kaha : hamein Leis ne abu-Zubair se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Jaabir (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne aik shakhs ko jo masjid mein kuchh teer bataur sadqa logon mein taqseem kar raha tha, hukm diya ke wo unko nokon se pakdey baghair unhein lekar ( logon ke darmyan mein se) na guzrey . ibne- Rumeh ne (apni riwayat mein) kaha : wo teeron ko bataur sadqa de raha tha."
6664,"Sabit ne abu-Barda se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs majlis ya bazar mein se guzrey aur uske hath mein teer hon to wo unhein unke paikaanon (naukdaar hisson) se pakdey, phir (tanbeeh hai) unke nokeeley hissey ki taraf se pakdey, phir (takeed hai) unke nokeeley hisson ki taraf se pakdey. kaha : to Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! (hamara ye haal hai ke) ham ne marney se pahley (apni usi zindagi mein) un teeron ko aik doosrey ke chehron ki taraf seedha kar liya hai."
6665,"Buraid ne abu-Barda se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab tum mein se koi shakhs hamari masjid ya hamarey bazar mein se guzrey aur uske paas teer hon to wo unhein apni hatheli se unke tez nokdaar hisson ki taraf se pakdey, kahin aisa na ho ke iska koi hissey musalmanon mein se kisi shakhs ko lag jaey. ya farmaya : wo unke paikaanon ko apni muththi mein pakdey ."
6666,"Ayub ne ( Muhammad ( Ibne-Sirin se riwayat ki, kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna ke abul-Qaasim (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jisne apne bhai ki taraf lohey ke kisi hathiyar se ishara kya to is par Farishtey laanat kartey rahtey hain yahan tak ke wo us kaam ko tark kar de, chahey wo uska maan-jaya bhai hi kyon na ho."
6667,"Ibne-Aun ne Muhammad (bin Sirin ( se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
6668,"Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat hai, kaha : ye hadisein hain jo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat kin, phir unhon-ne kai hadison zikr kin, unmein se aik ye hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum mein se koi shakhs apne bhai ki taraf hathiyar se ishara na karey, kyonke tum mein se koi shakhs nahi janta ke shayad shaitan achcha iske hath mein usey harkat de (aur wo doosrey musalman ko lag jaey) aur wo ( jiske hath se hathiyar chaley ( jahannam ke garhey mein gir jaey."
6669,"Abu-Bakar ke aazad karda ghulam Sumai ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik shakhs rastey par chala ja raha tha, usne rastey par aik kaantey daar tehni dekhi to usey (eik taraf) hata diya. Allah Taala ne usey iska inaam diya to uski bakhshish farma di."
6670,"Suhel ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik shakhs rastey ke uper padi hui darakht ki aik shaakh ke paas se guzra to usne kaha : Allah ki qism ! main us shaakh ko musalmanon ke rastey se hata dunga taake ye unko eza na de to us shakhs ko jannat mein dakhil kar diya gaya."
6671,"Aamash ne Abu-Saleh se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki, aap ne farmaya : maine aik shakhs ko dekha ke wo (is amal ke badley) jannat mein har taraf (nematon ke mazey) loot raha tha (kyonke) us ne rastey ke darmyan se aik aisey darakht ko kaat diya tha jo logon ko azeeyat deta tha."
6672,"abu-Raafe ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik darakht musalmanon ko azeeyat deta tha, chunanche aik shakhs aaya aur usey kaat diya to wo jannat mein dakhil ho gaya."
6673,"Aban bin Samaa ne kaha : mujhey abu-Waaze ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : mujhey Hazrat abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine kaha : Allah ke Nabi ! aap mujhey koi aisi baat sikha dein jisse main nafa hasil karun. aap ne farmaya : musalmanon ke rastey se takleef dene wali cheez ko hata diya karo."
6674,"Abu-Bakar bin Shuaib bin Habhaab ne abu-Waaze Raasbi se, unhon-ne Hazrat abu-Barza (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se kaha : Allah ke rasool! mein nahi janta, ho sakta hai ke aap ( duniya se) tashrif ley jayen aur main aap ke baad zinda reh jaun , isliye aap mujhey ( aakhirat ke safar ke liye) koi zaade-raah ata kar dijiye jis se Allah Taala mujhey nafa ata farmaai , Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : is tarah karo, is tarah karo. padhi. Abu-Bakar bin Shuaib un baton ko bhool gaey. padhi. aur (farmaya :) rastey se takleef deh chizon ko door kar diya karo."
6675,"Juweriya bin Asma ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin umr (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aurat ko billi ki wjah se azab diya gaya, us ne billi ko baandhey rakha yahan tak ke wo mar gaee to wo usi wjah se jahannam mein dakhil ho gaee, kyonke jab us ne billi ko baandha to na usko khilaaya, na pilaya aur na usko chhoda ke wo (khud hi) zamin ke keedey makodey kha leti."
6676,"imam Malik-bin-Anas ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se, Juweriya ki hadis ke ham mana riwayat ki."
6677,"Ubaidullah-bin-Umar ne Naafe se, unhon-ne Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aurat ko billi ke sabab azab diya gaya jisey usne baandh rakha tha, us ne usey khaney ko diya na peeney ko diya, na usey chhoda ke wo zamin ke keedey makodey shikar se kha leti ."
6678,Saeed Maqbari ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki.
6679,"Mamar ne hamein Hammam-bin-Munabba se riwayat ki, kaha : ye hadisein hamein Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se bayan kin, unhon-ne kai hadisein bayan kin, unmein se aik ye thi ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aurat apni billi ya billey ki wjah se dozakh mein chali gaee jis ko us ne baandh kar rakha tha, na khud usko khilaaya aur na usey chhoda ke zamin ke chhotey motey janwar chaba kha leti, yahan tak ke wo kamzor ho kar mar gaee."
6680,"Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri aur Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, donon ne kaha ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : izzat jalaal waaley Allah ka tehband hai aur badai us (ke kandhon ( ki chadar hai. jo shakhs in ( sifaat (ke mamley mein mere madde-muqaabil mein aayega, main usey azab doonga."
6681,"abu-Imran jooni ne Hazrat Jundub (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aik aadmi ne kaha : Allah ki qasam! Allah Taala falan shakhs ko nahi bakhshnega, to Allah Taala ne farmaya : kon hai jo mujh par qism kha raha hai ke main falan ko nahi bakhshunga? maine (is ( falan ko to bakhsh diya aur (aisa kehney waley! ( terey sarey amal zaaye kar diye. ya jin alfaz mein Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne irshad farmaya."
6682,"Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : bahut se ghubaar mein atey huey ( ghareebul-watan musaafir) bikhrey huey baalon waale, darwazon se dhutkaar diye janey waley log aisey hain ke agar unmein se koi Allah Taala par (aitimaad karke) qism kha ley to Allah Taala uski qism poori kar deta hai."
6683,"Hammad bin abi Salma aur Imam Malik ne Suhel bin abi Saleh se, unhon-ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab aik shakhs (ye) kehta hai : log halaak ho gaey to wo unhein halaak kar deta hai. (Imam Muslim ke aik shagird ( Abu-Ishaq ne kaha : mujhey (yaqeeni taur par) malum nahi ke (kaaf ke) zabar ke sath ( اهلكهم ( (is ne unhein halaak kar diya hai) ya pesh ke sath ( اهلكهم ( (un sabse badh kar halaak karne wala hai)."
6684,Rooh bin-Qasim aur Sulaiman-bin Bilal ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki.
6685,"Malik-bin-Anas, Lais-bin-Sad aur Yazid-bin-Harun sab ne Yahya-bin-Saeed se riwayat ki, (usi tarah) Muhammad-bin-Musanna ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz unhi ke hain. padhi. kaha : hamein abdul-wahaab Saqafi ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : maine Yahya-bin-Saeed se suna, kaha : mujhey Abu-Bakar bin Muhammad-bin Amr bin Hazam ne khabar di ke Umra ne unko hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se suna, wo kehti thin : maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko ye farmatey huey suna : mujhey Jibreel musalsal hamsaaey ke sath husne-sulook ke liye kehtey rahe, yahan tak ke mujhey yaqin honey laga ke wo zaroor unhein wiraasat mein Sharik kar dengey."
6686,"Hisham-bin-Urwa ne apne walid se, unhon-ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6687,Umar-bin Muhammad ke walid ne kaha : maine Hazrat ibne-Umar (Raziallahu anhu) ko ye kehtey huey suna : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Jibreel mujhey lagaataar hamsaaey ke sath husne-suluk ki talqeen kartey rahe yahan tak ke mujhey yaqin honey laga ke wo usey waaris ( bhi) bana dengey.
6688,"Abdul-Azeez bin Abdus-Samad Ami ne kaha : hamein abu-Imran Jawni ne Abdullah-bin Samit se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : Abu-Zar! jab tum shorba pakaao to usmein pani zyada rakho aur apne padausiyon ko yad rakho."
6689,"Shoba ne abu-Imran Jawni se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Samit se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : mere khaleel (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujhey wasiiyat ki : jab tum shorbey wala saalan pakaao to usmein pani zyada rakho, phir apne hamsaayon mein se kisi (zarurat mand) gharaaney ko dekho aur is mein se kuchh achchhey tareeqey se unko bhijwa do."
6690,"Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne mujh se farmaya : neki mein kisi cheez ko haqeer na samjho, chahey yahi ho ke tum apne (musalman) bhai ko khultey huey chehrey se milo."
6691,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas jab koi zarurat mand aata to aap apne sath baithey huey logon ki taraf mutwajjeh hotey aur farmatey : tum (bhi uski) shafaat karo, tumhen bhi ajr diya jaeyga aur Allah Taala apne Nabi ki zaban se wahi faisla jari karaaega jo usko pasand hoga."
6692,"Hazrat abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : nek padaus aur burey padaus ki misal mushk bechnewale aur bhattii dhonkney waley ki tarah hai, mushk bechnewale ya tum ko hadiye mein mushk de dega ya tum us se khareed logey, warna kam se kam tumhen us se achi khushbu aaeygi aur bhatti dhonkney wala ya to (chingaariyon se) tumharey kapdey jalaaeyga ya tumhen (is se) badboo aaeygi."
6693,"Mamar aur Shuaib ne ibne-Shahab Zohri se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Abdullah-bin abi-Bakr bin Hazam ne hadis bayan ki, unhein Urwa-bin-Zubair ne bataya ke Ummul-Momenin Aaisha Siddiqa (Raziallahu anha) ne kaha : mere paas aik aurat aai, uske sath uski 2 betiyaan bhi thin, us ne mujh se (khana) maanga to usey mere paas aik khajoor ke siwa aur kuchh na mila. maine wahi usko de di, us ne wo khajoor lekar apni 2 betiyon mein taqseem kar di aur khud usmein se kuchh na khana, phir wo khadi hui, aur wo uski donon betiyaan chali gain, phir Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) mere paas tashrif laey to maine aapko us aurat ki baat batai to Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis kisi par betiyon ki parwarish ka baar pad jaey aur wo unke sath husne-sulook karey to wo uske liye jahannam se ( bachaney wala ( parda hongi ."
6694,"Irak bin Malik ne Hazrat Aaisha (Raziallahu anha) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mere paas aik miskeen aurat aai jisne apni 2 betiyaan uthai hui thin, maine usko teen khajoorein din, usne unmein se har aik ko eik-eik khajoor di, (bachi hui) aik khajoor khaney ke liye apne munh ki taraf ley gaee, to wo bhi uski 2 betiyon ne khaney ke liye maang li, us ne wo khajoor bhi jo wo khana chahti thi, 2 hissey karke donon betiyon ko de di. mujhey iska ye kaam bahut achchha laga. maine Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ko bataya to aap ne farmaya : Allah ne is (amal ( ki wjah se uske liye jannat pakki kar di hai ya ( farmaya : (us wjah se usey aag se aazad kar diya hai."
6695,"Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat hai, Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jis shakhs ne 2 ladkiyon ki unke baligh honey tak parwarish ki, qiyamat ke din wo aur main is tarah aaeingey aur Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne apni ungliyon ko milaaya."
6696,"Imam Malik ne ibne-Shahab se, unhon-ne Saeed-bin-Musaiyab se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki ke aap ne farmaya : jis kisi musalman ke teen bachchey faut ho jayen to usey aag sirf qism pura karne ke liye chhueygi."
6697,"Sufiyan aur Mamar donon ne Zohri se Malik ki sanad ke sath unhi ke mafhoom mein hadis bayan ki, magar Sufiyan ki hadis mein hai : to wo sirf qism poori karne ke liye aag mein dakhil hoga."
6698,Suhel ke walid ( Abu-Saleh ( ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne Ansar ki aurton se farmaya : tum mein se jis aurat ke bhi teen bachchey faut ho jayen aur wo un ( par sabr kartey huey un (ka sawab Allah se talab karey to wo zaroor jannat mein dakhil hogi. unmein se aik aurat ne kaha : ya 2 ( bachchey faut ho jayen?) Allah ke rasool! to aap ne farmaya : ya 2 bachchey (faut ho jaaein.)
6699,"abu-Awana ne Abdur-Rehman bin Asbahani se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh Zakwan se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Saeed Khudri (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik aurat aai aur kaha : aap ki guftgu (ka bada hissey ( mard le gaey, lihaza aap hamarey liye bhi apni taraf se aik din muqarrar farma dein ke ham aap ke paas aaya karein aur Allah ne aapko jo sikhaya hai is mein se aap hamein bhi sikhaa dein. aap ne farmaya : tum auratein falan-falan din ikatthi ho jaanaa. khawaateen ikatthi ho gain to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) unke paas tashrif laey aur Allah ne jo ilm aapko ata farmaya tha usmein se unko bhi sikhaya, phir aap ne farmaya : tum mein se koi aurat nahi jo apne bachchon mein se teen bachchon ko apne aagey (Allah ke paas) rawaana kar de, magar wo uske liye aag se bachaney wala parda bin jaenge. aik aurat ne kaha : aur 2 bachchey bhi aur 2 bachchey bhi aur 2 bachchey bhi? to Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aur 2 bachchey bhi aur 2 bachchey bhi aur 2 bachchey bhii."
6700,"Muhammad-bin-Jafar aur Muaz ne kaha : hamein Shoba ne Abdur-Rehman bin Asbahani se isi sanad ke sath iske ham mana riwayat ki aur donon ne Shoba se (riwaayat kartey huey) mazeed ye kaha : Abdur-Rehman bin Asbahani se riwayat hai, unhon-ne kaha : maine abu-Hazim se suna, wo Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan kar rahe they, kaha : Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : teen bachchey jo bulooghat ki umr ko nahi pahunchey."
6701,"hamein Suwed-bin-Saeed aur Muhammad-bin Abdul-Aala ne hadis bayan ki. padhi. donon ke alfaz miltey-jultey hain. padhi. donon ne kaha : hamein Motamir (bin Sulaiman Taimi ( ne apne walid se riwayat ki, unhon-ne abu-Saleel se aur unhon-ne abu-Hassaan se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : maine Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se kaha : mere 2 bachchey faut ho gaey hain, aap hamein Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki kon si hadis suna saktey hain jis se aap hamein hamarey faut honey walon ke mutaalliq hamarey dilon ki tasalli dila sakein? ( abu-Hassaan ne) kaha : (hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : haan. (aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : ( chhotey bachchey jannat ke pani ke keedey hain (wo jannat ke andar hi rahtey hain) unmein se koi apne bap . padhi. ya farmaya : apne maan-baap ko milega to wo usey uske kapdey se pakad lega. padhi. ya kaha : uske hath se, jis tarah maine tumharey us kapdey ke kinarey se pakda hua hai, phir us waqt tak nahi hatega . padhi. ya kaha : nahi rukega, yahan tak ke Allah usey aur uske walid ko jannat mein dakhil kar dega aur Suwed ki riwayat main (abu-Saleel se riwayat hai ke bajaey yun) hai : hamein abu-Saleel ne hadis sunai."
6702,Yahya-bin-Saeed ne Taimi se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki aur kaha : aap ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se koi aisi baat suni hai jis se aap hamarey faut ho janey walon ke hawale se hamarey dilon ko tasalli dila sakein? (hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ne) kaha : haan.
6703,"abu-Bakar-bin-abi-Sheba , Muhammad-bin-Abdullah bin Numer aur abu-Saeed ashajj ne hamein hadis bayan ki. padhi. alfaz Abu-Bakar ke hain. padhi. unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hafs bin Ghiyas ne hadis bayan ki, neez hamein Umar-bin Hafs bin Ghiyas ne hadis bayan ki. unhon-ne kaha : hamein mere walid ne apne dada Talaq bin Muawiya se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Zaraa bin-Amr bin Jarir se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik aurat Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas apne bachchey ko lekar aai aur kaha : Allah ke Nabi ! Allah Taala se uske haq mein dua farmaiye, main teen bachchey dafn kar chuki hun. aap ne farmaya : tum ne teen ( bachchon ( ko dafn kya hai? usne kaha : ji haan , aap ne farmaya : tum ne dozakh se bchney ke liye aik mazbut baad laga di hai. umr (bin Hafs ( ne kaha : unhon-ne apne dada ( Talaq ( se riwayat ki aur baaqiyon ne kaha : Talaq se riwayat hai aur dada ka zikr nahi kya."
6704,"Qutaiba-bin-Saeed aur Zuhair-bin-Harab ne kaha : hamein Jarir ne Talaq bin Muawiya Nakhai abu-Ghayaas se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne Abu-Zaraa bin-Amr bin Jarir se aur unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik aurat apne betey ko lekar aai to usne kaha : Allah ke rasool! ye bimar hai aur main iske barey mein) sakht ( khof ka shikar hun, main (apne) teen bachchey dafn kar chuki hun, Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum ne dozakh se bchney ke liye mazbut baad bana li hai. Zuhair ne kaha : Talaq se riwayat hai aur kunniyat ( abu-Ghayaas (ka zikr nahi kya."
6705,"Jarir ne Suhel se, unhon-ne apne walid (Abu-Saleh) se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : jab Allah Taala kisi bandey se mohabbat karta hai to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko bulata hai aur farmata hai : main falan se mohabbat karta hun tum bhi us se mohabbat karo, kaha : to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) us se mohabbat kartey hain, phir wo aasman mein awaz detey hain, kehtey hain : Allah Taala falan shakhs se mohabbat karta hai, tum bhi us se mohabbat karo, chunanche aasman waley us se mohabbat kartey hain, kaha : phir uske liye zamin mein maqbooliyat rakh di jati hai, aur jab Allah Taala kisi bandey se bughz rakhta hai to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) ko bula kar farmata hai : main falan shakhs se bughz rakhta hun, tum bhi us se bughz rakho, to Jibreel (Alaihissalam) us se bughz rakhtey hain, phir wo aasman walon mein elaan kartey hain ke Allah Taala falan se bughz rakhta hai, tum bhi us se bughz rakho, kaha : to wo (sab) us se bughz rakhtey hain, phir uske liye zamin mein bhi bughz rakh diya jata hai."
6706,"Abdul-Azeez darawardi, Alaa bin Musaiyab aur imam Malik-bin-Anas sab ne Suhel se isi sanad ke sath riwayat ki, albatta Alaa bin Musaiyab ki hadis mein bughz ka zikr nahi hai) sirf mohabbat karne ki baat hai.)"
6707,"Abdul-Azeez bin-Abdullah-bin abi Salma maajishoon ne Suhel se, unhon-ne Abu-Saleh se riwayat ki, kaha : ham Arfa mein they ke Hazrat Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez ka wahan se guzar hua aur wo Haj ke ameer they, log khadey ho kar unhein dekhney lagey, maine apne walid se kaha : abba jaan! main ye dekh raha hun ke Allah Taala Umar-bin Abdul-Azeez se mohabbat karta hai, unhon-ne puchha : iska kya sabab hai? maine kaha : isliye ke logon ke dilon mein unki mohabbat paai jati hai, unhon (Abu-Saleh ( ne kaha : tera bap qurbaan ho ! tum ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki hadis suni hai. iske baad unhon-ne Suhel se Jarir ki riwayat ki hui hadis bayan ki."
6708,Abu-Saleh ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : roohein aik doosrey ke sath rehney wali jamatein hain. unmein se jo aik doosrey (ki aik jaisi sifaat ( se aagah ho gain unmein yakjaai ( الفت (ho gaee aur) sifaat ke ikhtilaf ki bina par) jo aik doosrey se gurezaan rahen wo aapasi mukhtalif ho gain.
6709,"Yazeed bin Asamm ne Hazrat Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) se marfooan aik hadis bayan ki, kaha : log soney chandi ki kanon ki tarah madaniyaat ki kaanein hain, jo zamana jahiliyat mein achchhey they wo agar Deen ko samajh lein to zamana Islam mein bhi achchhey hain. aur roohein aik sath rehney wali jamatein hain jo aapas mein (eik jaisi sifaat ki bina par) aik doosrey ko pahchaanney lagein unmein yakjaai paida ho gaee aur jo (sifaat ke ikhtilaf ki bina par) aik doosrey se gurezaan rahen, wo aapas mein mukhtalif ho gain."
6710,Ishaq bin-Abdullah-bin abi Talha ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki ke aik dehati ne Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha : qiyamat Kab aaeygi? Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne us se farmaya : tum ne uske liye kya taiyaar kar rakha hai? usne kaha : Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mohabbat. aap ne farmaya : tum usi ke sath hogey jis se tum ko mohabbat hai.
6711,"Sufiyan ne Zohri se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs ne puchha : Allah ke rasool! qiyamat Kab hogi ? aap ne farmaya : tum ne uske liye kya taiyaar ki hai? us ne zyada chizon ka zikr nahi kya, (chand aik kaamon ka zikr kar saka) usne kaha : aur lekin main Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mohabbat karta hun, aap ne farmaya : tum iske sath hogey jis se tumhen mohabbat hai."
6712,"Mamar ne Zohri se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : mujhey Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis sunai ke Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik dehati aaya, usi (pichhli hadis) ki tarah magar (is mein hai ke) usne kaha : maine uske liye kuchh zyada taiyaari nahi ki jis par main apni tareef kar sakun (lekin main Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mohabbat karta hun.)"
6713,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne kaha : hamein Sabit Bunani ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis bayan ki, unhon-ne kaha : aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki khidmat mein hazir hua aur kaha : Allah ke rasool! qiyamat Kab hogi? aap ne farmaya : tum ne uske liye kya taiyaar kya hai? usne kaha : Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ki mohabbat . Aap (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : tum usi ke sath hogey jis se tum ko mohabbat hogi. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : Islam qabool karne ke baad hamein Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke us irshad se badh kar aur kisi baat se itni khushi nahi hui : tum iske sath hogey jis se tum ko mohabbat hogi. Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ne kaha : main Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) aur Abu-Bakar aur umr (Raziallahu anhu) se mohabbat karta hun aur mujhey ummeed hai ke main unke sath hunga, har chand ke maine unki tarah amal nahi kiye."
6714,"Jafar bin Sulaiman ne hamein hadis sunai, kaha : hamein Sabit Bunani ne Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) se hadis sunai, unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se riwayat ki aur unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) ka ye qaul ke main ( Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam)) se mohabbat karta hun, aur uske baad wali baat bayan nahi ki."
6715,"Mansoor ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : hamein Hazrat Anas-bin-Malik (Raziallahu anhu) ne hadis bayan ki, kaha : aik baar jab main aur Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) masjid se nikal rahe they, to masjid ki chaukhat ke paas hamari aik shakhs se mulaqat hui, usne kaha : Allah ke rasool! qiyamat Kab hai? aap ne farmaya : tum ne uske liye kya taiyaar kya hai? to jaisey wo thithak gaya, phir usne kaha : Allah ke rasool! maine uske liye bahut zyada namazein, bahut zyada rozey aur bahut zyada sadqaat to taiyaar nahi kiye, lekin main Allah aur uske rasool (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se mohabbat rakhta hun, aap ne farmaya : tum usi ke sath hogey jis se tumhen mohabbat hogi."
6716,"Amr-bin-Murra ne Saalim-bin abi Jaad se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
6717,"abu-Awana , Shoba aur Hisham ne Qatada se, unhon-ne Hazrat Anas (Raziallahu anhu) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se yahi hadis riwayat ki."
6718,"Jarir ne ( Sulaiman ( Aamash se, unhon-ne abu-Waeil se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se riwayat ki, kaha : aik shakhs Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aaya, usne kaha : Allah ke rasool! aap us shakhs ko kaisey dekhtey hain jo kisi qaum se mohabbat karta hai magar abhi tak iske sath nahi mila? (aemal mein unse bahut peechhey hai) Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ne farmaya : aadmi usi ke sath hoga jis se wo mohabbat karta hai."
6719,"Shoba aur Sulaiman-bin-Qarm ne Sulaiman (Aamash) se, unhon-ne abu-Waeil se, unhon-ne Abdullah (bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu)) se aur unhon-ne Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se usi ki tarah riwayat ki."
6720,"abu-Muawia aur Muhammad-bin Ubaid ne Aamash se, unhon-ne ( abu-Waeil ( Shaqiq se aur unhon-ne abu-Musa (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, unhon-ne kaha : Nabi (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) ke paas aik shakhs aaya, phir Aamash se Jarir ki riwayat ki tarah hadis bayan ki."
6721,"Hammad-bin-Zaid ne abu-Imran Joni se, unhon-ne Abdullah-bin Samit se, unhon-ne Hazrat Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) se riwayat ki, kaha : Rasulullah (Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam) se puchha gaya : aap ka kya khayal hai ke aik shakhs achchhey kaam karta hai aur log uski tareef kartey hain? aap ne farmaya : ye momin ke liye fauri basharat hai."
6722,"Wakee, Muhammad-bin-Jafar , Abdus-Samad aur Nazar sab ne Shoba se, unhon-ne abu-Imran Joni se Hammad-bin-Zaid ki sanad ke sath , usi ki hadis ki tarah riwayat ki, magar Shoba se Abdus-Samad ke siwa (baqi) sab ki hadis mein hai : aur log uski wjah se uske sath mohabbat kartey hain. aur Abdus-Samad ki hadis mein hai : aur log uski tareef kartey hain jis tarah Hammad ne kaha hai."
